        "generateUrl": "https://console.dbos.dev/settings/apikey",
        "setup": "In the [DBOS Console](https://console.dbos.dev), register your application if needed, then open the [API key settings page](https://console.dbos.dev/settings/apikey) to create a scoped API key. The docs say API keys can be scoped by permissions and application, do not expire by default, and are supplied to apps via `DBOS_CONDUCTOR_KEY` or to HTTP calls as `Authorization: Bearer dbos_...`.",
